      "comment": "ETHANOL SECRET (3) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before boxing on well and holding a 6 length second (34.48) at this track over 600m in a Grade 5. Key player on best form. URANA PARALLAX (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (34.32) in a Grade 4/5 at Sandown. Form here sound including two wins. Can figure in the finish. FAST REPLY (5) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (35.18) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can find the frame this time. BACARDI GIRL (1) returns here with a good chance to improve on last time.",
